{"title":"父亲的茶罐","authors":["萧建春"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":11,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的茶罐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧建春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的青铜茶罐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子没有理由拒绝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝不下大碗“广西茶”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就掌不了大犁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就找不到能干健壮的老婆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就挑不起艰难沉重的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不能在六月的阳光下曝晒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑溜溜的背脊上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就淌不下亮晶晶的汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潇洒的牛鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩不出清脆的回响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田里长不出茁壮的日子……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的青铜茶罐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经是一个甜甜的谜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一天抑制不住激动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛地喝下谜底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼泪苦下来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舌头涩厚了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子开始渐渐明白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲是苦水浇铸的汉子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的日子始终是咸的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的日子始终是涩的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能拒绝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的咸和涩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从烈日里走进树荫下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一气连喝三大碗“广西茶”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼噜呼噜蝉鸣般悠扬的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把智慧的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播进土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幻化为澄黄澄黄的香浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰的鼾声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为来年的春雷"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}